java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
public class CanonicizeStepPanel
extends StepPanel

This panel represents a single step in a multi-step process, both graphically and logically. It encapsulates all the necessary graphical elements and program logic needed for this step, and provides access methods for necessary data to be passed along to the next step. Specifically, it handles Canonicizer processing for the JGAAP program.

Author:
Chuck Liddell Created 11/12/08 TODO: Complex Canonicizer data model and visual representation. Drag and Drop, the works.
